citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:20 am to
11:50 am on 28-Jan-20.
Attempts to make contact with the licensee were done by knocking on the door, honking the GOV's horn, calling the
licensee's phone number, leaving a voicemail and waiting in the driveway for 30 minutes.
